  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The hardcoded timeout on getPayload is defaulted at 4 seconds for MEV-boost but some consensus clients, such as [Prysm](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/pull/11413) and Teku, are defaulting to 3 seconds. Should we try to align these or are there other reasons they are/should be different?",
